Food Truck Face Off - Season 1, Episode 7




The Distillery District Duel

Jesse Palmer puts two teams of food truck hopefuls through their paces in the historic Distillery District in Toronto, Canada, on Sell Day One, where one team is reduced to tears while another is too cocky for their own good. They'll have to double down for Sell Day Two to draw in customers while selling alongside established food trucks.




Original Air Date: 06-Nov-2014
